video_title: Agents Unleashed Podcast Ep. 2 - User-Owned AI: Where We're At, Where We're Going ft. David Minarsch
description:
Welcome back! This is the second episode of the Agents Unleashed podcast, and this time, it's an interview with David Minarsch, Co-founder and CEO of Valory and founding member of the Olas DAO.  

This conversation focused on the current "state of AI agents" with a focus on user-ownership of AI.

Chapters

00:00 Introduction to episode and guest David Minarsch
01:46 Evolution from basic agents to LLM-powered systems
08:54 Comparing Web2 and Web3 agent capabilities
11:13 Olas mission and importance of agent ownership
13:48 Understanding the emerging agent economy
17:42 Impact of model commodification on agent development
19:30 Specialization and interaction between AI agents
21:00 Privacy challenges and blockchain solutions
24:00 Future outlook for AI agent adoption
25:24 Call to action and closing remarks


Agents Unleashed is an ongoing event series focused on AI agents. Events have been held in 6 cities and counting, with 77+ speakers and over 2500 total attendees. To find out more about the next event, head to https://olas.network/agents-unleashed. 

Sponsored by Olas, the best way to own and monetize your AI agents. Get the details at https://www.olas.network 

Theme music: "Forward" by Grand Project on Pixabay: https://pixabay.com/users/grand_project-19033897/
